                              "content": "醫療業：AI 輔助診斷系統使早期癌症檢出率提升 28%，診斷時間縮短 60%",
                              "lineHeight": 1.6,
                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                              "fontSize": 14,
                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "EeV7B",
                      "name": "highlightBlock",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "fill": "#1A1A1A",
                      "stroke": {
                        "align": "inside",
                        "thickness": {
                          "left": 2
                        },
                        "fill": "#C9A962"
                      },
                      "padding": 16,
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "0AEyv",
                          "name": "highlightText",
                          "fill": "#B0B0B0",
                          "content": "「到 2027 年，全球企業 AI 支出預計達到 5,000 億美元，其中 62% 將用於生成式 AI 應用的部署與擴展。」— McKinsey Global Institute",
                          "lineHeight": 1.6,
                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                          "fontSize": 14,
                          "fontWeight": "normal",
                          "fontStyle": "italic"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "u4nFA",
                      "name": "h2b",
                      "fill": "white",
                      "content": "產業影響",
                      "fontFamily": "Cormorant Garamond",
                      "fontSize": 22,
                      "fontWeight": "600"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "XLL9T",
                      "name": "para2",
                      "fill": "#B0B0B0",
                      "content": "AI 對傳統產業的衝擊不僅限於效率提升。更深層的變革在於它正重新定義價值創造的方式——從產品導向轉向數據導向、從規模經濟轉向智能經濟。企業若無法在 2026 年前完成 AI 策略佈局，將面臨被市場淘汰的風險。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "2EDaP",
